    "created_at": "2024-07-15T23:37:43Z",
    "updated_at": "2024-07-15T23:37:43Z",
    "body": "Had the same problem in my setup, documenting more explicitly here.  You will need to reload your session to apply the changes. \r\n\r\n```bash\r\ngit clone --recursive --depth 1 --shallow-submodules https://github.com/akinomyoga/ble.sh.git\r\nmake -C ble.sh install PREFIX=~/.local\r\necho 'source ~/.local/share/blesh/ble.sh' >> ~/.bashrc\r\n```\r\n\r\n",
    "author_association": "NONE",
